"{\"uid\": \"thedrum.com-industry-insight-the-attention-olympics-how-brands-can-win-gold-capturing-consumer-attention-using-ooh\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Advertisement Member article This content is produced by a member of The Drum Network, a paid-for membership club for CEOs and their agencies who want to share their expertise and grow their business.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 103, \"end\": 111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Drum_(TV_program)\", \"score\": 0.5711775043632158, \"rank\": 0.6639053254437071, \"text\": \"The Drum\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Drum_(TV_program)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Drum_(TV_program)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Advertisement Member article\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 28}, {\"ngram\": \"This content\", \"from\": 29, \"to\": 41}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 57, \"to\": 65}, {\"ngram\": \"The Drum Network\", \"from\": 69, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"CEOs\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 122}, {\"ngram\": \"their agencies\", \"from\": 127, \"to\": 141}, {\"ngram\": \"their expertise\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 175}, {\"ngram\": \"their business\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"July 31, 2024|5 min read Listen to article4 min Dan Dawson, chief creative officer at Grand Visual - part of Talon - shares how you can find more mindful and entertaining ways to capture attention using OOH.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 350, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Dawson\", \"score\": 0.9999999983906491, \"rank\": 1.6090765123171018e-09, \"text\": \"Dan Dawson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Dawson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dan_Dawson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"2024|5 min\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 319}, {\"ngram\": \"chief creative officer\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 382}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Visual - part\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 405}, {\"ngram\": \"Talon - shares\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"more mindful and entertaining ways\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 475}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"OOH\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We live in busy times.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"busy times\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our digital and media footprints are bigger and more varied than ever, and our daily lives often seem like an open invitation for brands to make a grab for our attention at any and every moment.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our digital and media footprints\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"our daily lives\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"an open invitation\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"brands\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"a grab\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"our attention\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 703}, {\"ngram\": \"every moment\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Addictive behaviors like swiping and scrolling have hooked us, sending more and more people to ad-blocking platforms and digital detoxes in a bid to reclaim their attention.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Addictive behaviors\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"more and more people\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"ad-blocking platforms\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"digital detoxes\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"a bid\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"their attention\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, as we all know, the lure of the social feed is hard to resist in the long term.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lure\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"the social feed\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"the long term\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brands have no choice but to lean into the attention economy, so one of the answers - if you want to keep consumers on board - is to find more mindful and entertaining ways to command attention that do not leave your audience feeling empty and listless.\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brands\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"no choice\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1011}, {\"ngram\": \"the attention economy\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"the answers\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"consumers\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"board\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"more mindful and entertaining ways\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"your audience\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The real winners will be the brands who combine real-life activations with digital experiences to produce a powerful blend of authenticity, surprise and craft, supercharging responses in a positive way.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The real winners\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"the brands\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"real-life activations\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"digital experiences\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerful blend\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"authenticity\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"surprise\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"craft\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"responses\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive way\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As people remember only 10% of what they see but 90% of what they do (estimation my own), we have unique opportunities in theout of home (OOH)space to bring the audience in and make them part of an experience, to immerse them in our world for a brief moment.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"only 10%\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"90%\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"(estimation\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"unique opportunities\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1584}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"an experience\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"our world\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"a brief moment\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People are hungry for unique, shareable experiences that make them feel part of a brand's story, so whether it's through special builds,interactive digital displays, or clever use of data-driven messaging, the goal is to create moments that cut through the noise and forge emotional connections.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"unique, shareable experiences\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"a brand's story\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"special builds\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"data-driven messaging\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"the goal\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1921}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"the noise and forge emotional connections\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"OOH is well placed to deliver the kind of one-off, entertaining encounters that stop people in their tracks.\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"OOH\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"the kind\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"their tracks\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The convergence of creative optimization andprogrammatic advertisingallows for real-time adjustments to messaging that ensure relevance and results in maximum impact.\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The convergence\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"creative optimization andprogrammatic advertisingallows\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"real-time adjustments\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2213}, {\"ngram\": \"relevance\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2248}, {\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2260}, {\"ngram\": \"maximum impact\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get this right, and people will stop, look, and share the campaign - in the same way we photograph anything unexpected we might see as we move about our cities and our lives.\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \"the campaign\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"the same way\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"our cities\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"our lives\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The\\\"Should have gone to Specsavers\\\" vanwas placed to look as though the driver's eyesight wasn't up to scratch when he missed the sign that said 'Caution: No Parking,' leaving his van suspended on some moving bollards.\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Specsavers\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2490}, {\"ngram\": \"vanwas\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"the driver's eyesight\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2545}, {\"ngram\": \"scratch\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"the sign\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2590}, {\"ngram\": \"Caution\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"his van\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"some moving bollards\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This provided an unexpected street scene that inspired passers-by to stop, enjoy, film and share.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an unexpected street scene\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"passers\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When we startedGrand Visualback in 2005, we used the strapline \\\"Attention is important, but involvement is critical\\\".\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Visualback\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2805}, {\"ngram\": \"the strapline\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"Attention\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"involvement\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have since dropped the line, but the ethos and methodology for delivering against it has stayed with us, because we believe that context is critical: it's an opportunity to speak directly to a specific audience at a given time or location, or in response to data like traffic, train delays or the weather.\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"the ethos\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"methodology\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"that context\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3031}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"a specific audience\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3105}, {\"ngram\": \"a given time\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"location\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3133}, {\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3149}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3170}, {\"ngram\": \"train delays\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3184}, {\"ngram\": \"the weather\", \"from\": 3188, \"to\": 3199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our work for Google Mapsused real-time data spread across different neighbourhoods around New York to encourage audiences to explore their local area.\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3215, \"end\": 3221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9999999991241566, \"rank\": 8.692426227040514e-10, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 3292, \"end\": 3300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999931437742, \"rank\": 6.748986258191442e-09, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our work\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3210}, {\"ngram\": \"different neighbourhoods\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3284}, {\"ngram\": \"audiences\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3323}, {\"ngram\": \"their local area\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Messaging was based on location, time, temperature and day, and based on venue ratings and other first party data.\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Messaging\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3362}, {\"ngram\": \"location\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3384}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3390}, {\"ngram\": \"temperature\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3403}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3411}, {\"ngram\": \"venue ratings\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3439}, {\"ngram\": \"other first party data\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The campaign delivered helpful, entertaining and smart advertising that tapped into the mindset of an audience as they moved around the city.\", \"from\": 3468, \"to\": 3609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The campaign\", \"from\": 3468, \"to\": 3480}, {\"ngram\": \"helpful, entertaining and smart advertising\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3534}, {\"ngram\": \"the mindset\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3563}, {\"ngram\": \"an audience\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3578}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 3600, \"to\": 3608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This kind of targeting is getting ever more sophisticated and real-time.\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3683, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This kind\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3620}, {\"ngram\": \"ever more sophisticated and real-time\", \"from\": 3645, \"to\": 3682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pepsi, for example, captured the attention of commuters and visitors with their experiential activation withJCDecauxat London's Waterloo Station.\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3684, \"end\": 3689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepsi\", \"score\": 0.9704741291824667, \"rank\": 0.030424170958852595, \"text\": \"Pepsi\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepsi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepsi\"}, {\"begin\": 3803, \"end\": 3809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.999999999134161, \"rank\": 7.883282659585936e-10, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 3812, \"end\": 3820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Waterloo_station\", \"score\": 0.9992497981211043, \"rank\": 0.0007507650794353691, \"text\": \"Waterloo\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Waterloo_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Waterloo_station\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3702}, {\"ngram\": \"the attention\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3726}, {\"ngram\": \"commuters\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3739}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3752}, {\"ngram\": \"their experiential activation\", \"from\": 3758, \"to\": 3787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pop-up gave consumers the chance to try the new mango flavour drink and be in with the chance of winning a holiday, all by following a few simple steps, including social media engagement.\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 4021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pop-up\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3840}, {\"ngram\": \"consumers\", \"from\": 3846, \"to\": 3855}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 3866}, {\"ngram\": \"the new mango flavour drink\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3901}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3927}, {\"ngram\": \"a holiday\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3948}, {\"ngram\": \"a few simple steps\", \"from\": 3967, \"to\": 3985}, {\"ngram\": \"social media engagement\", \"from\": 3997, \"to\": 4020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"OOH is just one element of a changing consumer landscape, but to my mind, it's evolving even more rapidly right now than alternative media investments.\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"OOH\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4026}, {\"ngram\": \"just one element\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4046}, {\"ngram\": \"a changing consumer landscape\", \"from\": 4050, \"to\": 4079}, {\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 4088, \"to\": 4095}, {\"ngram\": \"alternative media investments\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the second half of 2024, with a calendar still full of global cultural, sporting, and political events, brands have unprecedented opportunities to create dynamic, relevant content that adapts to changing moments, mindsets, and audiences.\", \"from\": 4175, \"to\": 4415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second half\", \"from\": 4178, \"to\": 4193}, {\"ngram\": \"a calendar\", \"from\": 4208, \"to\": 4218}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting\", \"from\": 4250, \"to\": 4258}, {\"ngram\": \"political events\", \"from\": 4264, \"to\": 4280}, {\"ngram\": \"brands\", \"from\": 4282, \"to\": 4288}, {\"ngram\": \"unprecedented opportunities\", \"from\": 4294, \"to\": 4321}, {\"ngram\": \"dynamic, relevant content\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4357}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 4382, \"to\": 4389}, {\"ngram\": \"mindsets\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4399}, {\"ngram\": \"audiences\", \"from\": 4405, \"to\": 4414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When every scroll, swipe, and glance is a potential battleground for consumer attention, the victors will be those who offer more than just products or services.\", \"from\": 4417, \"to\": 4578, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every scroll\", \"from\": 4422, \"to\": 4434}, {\"ngram\": \"swipe\", \"from\": 4436, \"to\": 4441}, {\"ngram\": \"glance\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4453}, {\"ngram\": \"a potential battleground\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4481}, {\"ngram\": \"consumer attention\", \"from\": 4486, \"to\": 4504}, {\"ngram\": \"the victors\", \"from\": 4506, \"to\": 4517}, {\"ngram\": \"products\", \"from\": 4557, \"to\": 4565}, {\"ngram\": \"services\", \"from\": 4569, \"to\": 4577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will be the brands that enrich lives, spark joy, and become an integral part of the cultural conversation, seamlessly blending into and enhancing the consumer's world in meaningful ways.\", \"from\": 4579, \"to\": 4770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the brands\", \"from\": 4592, \"to\": 4602}, {\"ngram\": \"lives\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4620}, {\"ngram\": \"spark joy\", \"from\": 4622, \"to\": 4631}, {\"ngram\": \"an integral part\", \"from\": 4644, \"to\": 4660}, {\"ngram\": \"the cultural conversation\", \"from\": 4664, \"to\": 4689}, {\"ngram\": \"the consumer's world\", \"from\": 4730, \"to\": 4750}, {\"ngram\": \"meaningful ways\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, the brands that will thrive in the attention economy are those that understand a fundamental truth: attention is important, but involvement is critical.\", \"from\": 4772, \"to\": 4936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the brands\", \"from\": 4784, \"to\": 4794}, {\"ngram\": \"the attention economy\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 4836}, {\"ngram\": \"a fundamental truth\", \"from\": 4863, \"to\": 4882}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 4884, \"to\": 4893}, {\"ngram\": \"involvement\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 4923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By creating experiences that engage consumers on multiple levels - emotional, intellectual, and experiential - brands can build lasting relationships that transcend traditional advertising.\", \"from\": 4937, \"to\": 5126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"experiences\", \"from\": 4949, \"to\": 4960}, {\"ngram\": \"consumers\", \"from\": 4973, \"to\": 4982}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple levels\", \"from\": 4986, \"to\": 5001}, {\"ngram\": \"emotional, intellectual, and experiential - brands\", \"from\": 5004, \"to\": 5054}, {\"ngram\": \"lasting relationships\", \"from\": 5065, \"to\": 5086}, {\"ngram\": \"traditional advertising\", \"from\": 5102, \"to\": 5125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement\", \"from\": 5128, \"to\": 5141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}]}"